{"tid":2299373,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"｜銀臺路增患者　有線老闆邱達昌回應確診傳聞：唔好亂寫！","createTime":"2020-11-24T17:19:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T14:13:44.000Z","uid":5195,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f77c37a255ab540b75454d9e37d383df72bc2a99","tid":2299373,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T17:19:48.000Z","msg":"第四波新冠肺炎疫情繼續在本港上流社會延燒，有線電視老闆、遠東發展有限公司執行董事、主席兼行政總裁邱達昌的妻子邱吳惠平確診，二人居於清水灣銀臺路其中一幢豪宅。衞生署周二（24日 )公布的患者居所資料，顯示銀臺路再增一名患者，為66歲男子，被列為與本地個案有流行病學關連。<br />\n<br />\n66歲的邱達昌周二晚接受查詢時，未有回應是否確診，他只着記者「唔好亂寫！」《香港01》記者已向其名下公司查詢，午夜後仍未獲回覆。邱吳惠平屬「歌舞群組 」，衞生署周二公布再增54名患者，累計增至187人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ff9dbff81a0d683961543f9be294a80bf48fba7","tid":2299373,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T17:21:15.000Z","msg":"佢屋企好多人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0729053766990610101495b742ccd5b7fdc228fd","tid":2299373,"uid":180401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T17:23:17.000Z","msg":"🦆🦆🦆🦆🦆"},{"pid":"b354f64bff8c54660ed034d8eddb305144df5e30","tid":2299373,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T17:55:54.000Z","msg":"綠帽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d56985fff53ae3d14e00842b4fcba06c591b467","tid":2299373,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T18:14:33.000Z","msg":"邱老闆 呢個係01呀 唔係有線打嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b97fae18ca61468801f3cf68a8fda1ae739b0520","tid":2299373,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T18:20:50.000Z","msg":"有線新聞今次唔跪唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91acf150b034ec16ce5927380a1211f8d515eda4","tid":2299373,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T18:53:45.000Z","